FileUni CLI for iKuai v4 App Store local installation.

Highlights:
- Upload the matching `.ipkg` package in Applications -> App Store -> Local installation.
- Uses a dedicated runtime volume so your FileUni data persists across restarts.
- Opens the regular FileUni setup flow on first launch.

How to use:
1. Pick the `.ipkg` package that matches your iKuai CPU architecture.
2. Upload it in the iKuai Web UI and keep the default runtime volume path.
3. Open `http://<ikuai-ip>:<mapped-port>` to finish FileUni setup.

Project: https://github.com/FileUni/FileUni-Project
